What's cooler than going
to a strip club in the daytime?

14:07.514 --> 14:10.348
The girls aren't always hot,
but the mozzarella sticks are.

14:11.717 --> 14:14.018
(groans):
Uh... Yeah.

14:14.020 --> 14:15.653
You sound like me
two weeks ago.

14:15.655 --> 14:18.223
