I heard the name "lyndsey."

14:18.225 --> 14:20.124
(groans)

14:20.126 --> 14:21.559
Yeah, that's it.

14:21.561 --> 14:22.994
What's going on?

14:22.996 --> 14:24.929
To be honest, I, uh...

14:24.931 --> 14:27.232
Had a bit of a
breakup myself.

14:27.234 --> 14:28.499
Oh, geez.
Mm.

14:28.501 --> 14:30.702
And here I am whining
about <i>my</i> problems.

14:30.704 --> 14:32.136
Eh.
I'm sorry, jeff.

14:32.138 --> 14:33.838
If I have a flaw,
it's that sometimes

14:33.840 --> 14:36.341
I'm not aware of things
that are going on around me.

14:36.343 --> 14:40.378
It's actually one of the
things I like most about you.

14:40.380 --> 14:42.213
So, what happened
between you and your girl?

14:42.215 --> 14:44.115
Well, she wanted
to get married,

14:44.117 --> 14:46.050
And I'm just not
sure I'm ready.

14:46.052 --> 14:48.453
No way! That's the same
reason I lost lyndsey.

14:48.455 --> 14:50.688
It's like we were
dating the same woman.

14:50.690 --> 14:53.324
It's exactly like that.

14:53.326 --> 14:55.593
So, do you miss her?
Are you kidding?

14:55.595 --> 14:57.195
I mean, she's the
only one for me.

14:57.197 --> 14:59.964
I mean, she's the one who
brings me up when I'm down...

14:59.966 --> 15:03.234
Whoa. Hello, future
mrs. Strongman.

15:03.236 --> 15:05.336
So, what are you
afraid of?

15:05.338 --> 15:07.572
I don't know.
It's just such a big commitment.

15:07.574 --> 15:09.407
Bottom line:
Do you still love her?

15:09.409 --> 15:11.676
Yes, I do.

15:11.678 --> 15:12.977
Then you got to
get her back.

15:12.979 --> 15:14.279
Don't make
the same mistake I did.

15:14.281 --> 15:15.313
Yeah, maybe you're right.

15:15.315 --> 15:16.881
I know I'm right.
Chances like this

15:16.883 --> 15:18.616
Only come along
once in a lifetime.

15:18.618 --> 15:20.318
I'm gonna do it, larry.

15:20.320 --> 15:22.754
I am gonna ask her to marry me.

15:22.756 --> 15:24.188
That-a-boy! And when
things work out,

15:24.190 --> 15:26.791
I'm gonna be the best man
at you and your girl's wedding.

15:26.793 --> 15:30.395
Well... We'll cross that
bridge when we come to it.

15:31.363 --> 15:32.864
Want a private
dance?

15:32.866 --> 15:35.833
Oh, sorry, I can't.
I have a date with destiny.

15:35.835 --> 15:38.136
Destiny's off today.

15:38.138 --> 15:40.638
Oh, no, I-I meant, uh, uh...
Never mind.

15:40.640 --> 15:43.074
Why don't you take my friend.
It's on me.

15:43.076 --> 15:44.676
Oh, I only have a 20.

15:44.678 --> 15:46.411
Uh, you know what?

15:46.413 --> 15:48.646
I think seven's fair.

15:51.951 --> 15:54.018
(machine buzzing)

15:56.555 --> 15:58.022
Walden?

15:58.024 --> 15:59.724
Oh, hey!

15:59.726 --> 16:01.359
Sorry, ladies!

16:01.361 --> 16:03.461
(machine stops)
man at work!

16:03.463 --> 16:05.029
Wh-what are you doing?

16:05.031 --> 16:09.267
Well, it's a little technical
for the layperson.

16:09.269 --> 16:11.803
What the hell, let me
walk you through it.

16:11.805 --> 16:14.872
What I'm doing is
sanding and re-staining,

16:14.874 --> 16:17.608
When I recognized some
dry rot and termite damage.

16:17.610 --> 16:19.777
And I thought to myself,
what the hell,

16:19.779 --> 16:21.479
I got a couple hours--

16:21.481 --> 16:24.749
Why don't I just rebuild
this bad boy from scratch.

16:26.385 --> 16:27.952
(giggles)

16:27.954 --> 16:30.221
The bubbles tickle my nose.

16:30.223 --> 16:32.457
Okay, you know what? You got
to stop building things.

16:32.459 --> 16:34.058
I was wrong--
you are so manly

16:34.060 --> 16:36.661
That if I were straight, I'd
totally bang your brains out.

16:36.663 --> 16:38.096
Well, of course you would,
sweetheart.

16:38.098 --> 16:39.764
But I'd probably
sleep with you once

16:39.766 --> 16:41.199
And then never call you again.

16:41.201 --> 16:42.266
Hold still, please.

16:43.502 --> 16:45.670
Yep, they're level.
(clears throat)

16:47.573 --> 16:49.640
(machine starts)
ow!

16:49.642 --> 16:51.843
Aah! Aah!

16:51.845 --> 16:53.478
Mmm.

16:53.480 --> 16:56.881
I'm just gonna rub some dirt
in it and keep going.

16:56.883 --> 16:58.816
Walden! Hey...

16:58.818 --> 17:00.151
What are you doing?

17:00.153 --> 17:01.986
Oh, this? Well,

17:01.988 --> 17:04.355
It's pretty technical
for the layperson.

17:04.357 --> 17:05.857
What the hell, let me just...

17:05.859 --> 17:07.492
No, doesn't matter,
doesn't matter.

17:07.494 --> 17:09.427
Uh, I-I got big news.

17:09.429 --> 17:12.497
I am gonna ask lyndsey
to marry me.

17:12.499 --> 17:13.931
Are you serious?

17:13.933 --> 17:15.733
Yeah, I just have to get a ring.

17:15.735 --> 17:17.368
I got a ring you could have.

17:17.370 --> 17:19.070
The one I proposed to zoey with.

17:19.072 --> 17:20.738
I don't know,
that ring didn't work.

17:20.740 --> 17:22.206
Neither do you.

17:22.208 --> 17:23.775
(chuckles):
Touché.

17:23.777 --> 17:27.111
Well, I can't believe my
best friend's getting married.

17:27.113 --> 17:29.180
All right, come on,
bring it in.

17:29.182 --> 17:30.348
Man hug.

17:30.350 --> 17:31.949
Oh. Oh. You smell.

17:31.951 --> 17:33.751
Oh, yeah.
It's awesome, isn't it?

17:33.753 --> 17:35.453
I haven't showered in two days.

17:35.455 --> 17:38.089
That's what guys do--
we stank.

17:39.691 --> 17:41.192
You smell good...

17:41.194 --> 17:42.393
Bitch.

17:49.902 --> 17:51.903
Ladies love flowers.

17:51.905 --> 17:53.404
Um...

18:03.882 --> 18:06.150
Oh, hey, jeff!

18:06.152 --> 18:07.885
Why are you calling me jeff?

18:07.887 --> 18:09.787
You must be here to see
your friend larry,

18:09.789 --> 18:11.756
Who is also here.

18:11.758 --> 18:14.225
Jeff? What are you
doing here?

18:14.227 --> 18:15.493
(laughs):
Larry!

18:15.495 --> 18:18.329
I-I just, uh, I
came by to-to...

18:18.331 --> 18:20.531
Yell at this one
over here

18:20.533 --> 18:22.700
For breaking up with
my friend larry.

18:22.702 --> 18:25.470
Can you think of a better
reason for me to drop by?

18:25.472 --> 18:28.039
'cause I certainly can't.

18:28.041 --> 18:30.141
Well, now that you're here, why
don't you have a drink with us.

18:30.143 --> 18:33.077
Oh, I-I'm sure jeff has
better places to be.

18:33.079 --> 18:34.946
Work, nope.
Girlfriend, nope.

18:34.948 --> 18:36.881
Taste in jewelry, nope.

18:36.883 --> 18:38.649
Here you go.

18:38.651 --> 18:40.418
Bottoms up, lyndsey.

18:40.420 --> 18:43.254
Not the first time
I've said <i>that</i> to her.

18:43.256 --> 18:44.555
(groans)

18:44.557 --> 18:46.190
What's this?

18:46.192 --> 18:47.592
A ring?

18:48.494 --> 18:50.094
What's going on?

18:51.029 --> 18:54.599
Yeah, what
<i>is</i> going on?

18:54.601 --> 18:57.401
Jeff helped me realize
I don't want to lose you.

18:57.403 --> 18:58.836
These last two weeks

18:58.838 --> 19:00.738
Have been the worst
in my life.

19:00.740 --> 19:02.173
I don't want to spend

19:02.175 --> 19:03.674
Another minute without you.

19:03.676 --> 19:04.909
Okay, I think
she's heard enough.

19:04.911 --> 19:06.410
Let's go get some
wings. Come on.

19:06.412 --> 19:07.678
Ooh, wings.

19:07.680 --> 19:09.647
Just let me
wrap this up real quick.

19:11.850 --> 19:14.986
Lyndsey macelroy,
you're my soul mate.

19:14.988 --> 19:17.121
Will you marry me?

19:17.123 --> 19:18.556
I can't believe
this is happening.

19:18.558 --> 19:20.758
Yes, yes, I will marry you!

19:23.662 --> 19:26.597
So, jeff, how'd it go
with <i>your</i> girl?

19:26.599 --> 19:27.899
Uh...

19:27.901 --> 19:29.600
I was too late.

19:29.602 --> 19:31.669
She's marrying someone else.

19:31.671 --> 19:34.272
That was quick.
Wasn't it?

19:34.274 --> 19:36.340
I'm sorry.

19:36.342 --> 19:38.676
Larry: You know what?
Forget her.

19:38.678 --> 19:42.480
If she chose some jackass over
you, she's just a dumb whore.

19:44.116 --> 19:46.184
Uh, she's-she's
actually really great.

19:46.186 --> 19:47.318
No, she's not.

19:47.320 --> 19:50.621
